query:
INSERT INTO folders (
                id,
                workspace_id,
                folder_id,
                name,
                sort_priority
            )
            VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
            ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
               updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
               name = excluded.name,
               folder_id = excluded.folder_id,
               sort_priority = excluded.sort_priority
